videos.description: Rae Burrell makes a nice bounce pass to Jordan Walker, who is able to sink the basket while drawing a foul.

videos.headline: Walker sinks and-1 bucket for Tennessee

videos.description: Rennia Davis gets the ball and sinks a nice jumper to give Tennessee a bigger lead over South Carolina.

videos.headline: Davis' contested jumper increases Tennessee's lead

videos.description: Kellie Harper tells SEC Now that she believes her halftime oration helped No. 21 Tennessee turn it around to upset No. 2 South Carolina, 75-67.
videos.headline: Harper's 'fiery' speech lights UT's fuse vs. Gamecocks

videos.description: Rennia Davis fuels No. 21 Tennessee's huge 75-67 upset of No. 2 South Carolina with 24 second-half points and 12 rebounds.
videos.headline: Lady Vols snap South Carolina's 31-game SEC win streak
